---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '@components/Hero.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Training">
  <Hero eyebrow="Training" title="Inclusive sessions for different goals." text="Qualified Coaches and Run Leaders support sessions that help members get the most from their running, whether they are chasing a PB or running with friends." primaryHref="/calendar/" primaryLabel="View calendar" secondaryHref="/join/" secondaryLabel="Try a session" />
  <section class="section section--white"><div class="container grid grid--3"><article class="card"><span class="badge">When</span><h3>Tuesday and Thursday</h3><p>The club generally meets from 6:30pm on Tuesday and Thursday evenings.</p></article><article class="card"><span class="badge">Where</span><h3>Wisbech Rugby Club</h3><p>Most sessions begin at Wisbech Rugby Club, although some are held elsewhere.</p></article><article class="card"><span class="badge">How</span><h3>Groups and shared sessions</h3><p>Sessions either have multiple groups or are arranged so everyone can work together.</p></article></div></section>
  <section class="section"><div class="container prose"><h2>What to expect</h2><p>Faster groups may run a little further and a little faster, but groups generally follow the same session theme. The aim is to make training useful and inclusive for all members.</p><p>New runners should contact the club before attending so the right session and group can be suggested.</p><p class="callout"><strong>TODO:</strong> add a typical monthly training pattern once confirmed by coaches.</p></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
